---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Thoughts">
	<div class="thoughts">
		<h1>Thoughts</h1>
		<div class="thought-list">
			<article class="thought">
				<h2>Digital Minimalism</h2>
				<div class="metadata">
					<span class="date">April 12, 2024</span>
					<span class="reading-time">5 min read</span>
				</div>
				<p>
					In a world of constant notifications and endless scrolling, I've been exploring the concept of digital minimalism. 
					It's not about completely disconnecting, but rather about being intentional with our digital interactions...
				</p>
				<a href="/thoughts/digital-minimalism" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
			</article>

			<article class="thought">
				<h2>The Art of Slow Living</h2>
				<div class="metadata">
					<span class="date">April 5, 2024</span>
					<span class="reading-time">4 min read</span>
				</div>
				<p>
					Lately, I've been contemplating the beauty of slowing down. In our fast-paced world, there's something 
					revolutionary about choosing to live life at a more deliberate pace...
				</p>
				<a href="/thoughts/slow-living" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.thoughts {
		max-width: 700px;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: var(--accent-color);
	}
	.thought-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}
	.thought {
		background: white;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	.thought h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--accent-color);
	}
	.metadata {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #666;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.thought p {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.read-more {
		color: var(--accent-color);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
	}
	.read-more:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>